  "intent": "Perform automated DNA isolation from whole blood samples using magnetic bead purification. Add 130\u00b5L starting buffer to magnetic plate wells, followed by 410\u00b5L lysis buffer (300\u00b5L to well top, 110\u00b5L into well) with 3x mixing cycles. Execute 5-minute room temperature incubation, then 2-minute magnetic separation at 14mm height. Remove 640\u00b5L supernatant, then perform three sequential wash cycles using reservoir wells A4-A10, each involving 600\u00b5L wash buffer addition, mixing, magnetic separation, and supernatant removal. Transfer plate to temperature module at 60\u00b0C, add 50\u00b5L elution buffer, incubate 10 minutes, return to magnetic deck for final separation, then transfer 50\u00b5L purified DNA to PCR plate.",
